Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,紧张过头了  反而能睡得很香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦  赶紧收拾准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,安迪  好久没参加个人大赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,请你见证我胜出  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,慢走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  你忘了带上爸爸亲手制作的肉肉便当
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说来  我最近一直没去看律舞的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔去看一次也不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  你看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是美音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在海外大赛上也连战连胜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有了美音和爱良为我加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要大展身手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,要的就是这种气势
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,咦  久里须要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在俄罗斯的新人赛上获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,临时决定参加冬日白雪杯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,久里须要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕是本次大赛上最大的竞争对手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题  没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,无论谁出战  我只跳好自己的Show
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那种气势  律舞没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,久里须要  那孩子的教练绝对是神崎其方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,响
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你们也在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么说可不对了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是来为小要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:05:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便也嘲笑你一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么说太没礼貌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是来给阿响做保镖的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不能惹上关东的虫子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,花音满面笑容时就是她怒气冲天的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那就再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,再见  要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,花音  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,花音  妨碍我难得的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可是  响来为我加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我的心灵已经充满电了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,用恋爱的力量努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,行  交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,听说小要的教练可能是律舞的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不是该告诉她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还不知道是不是真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,先别告诉她比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,爱良
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,爱良
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,小要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好久没闻到你的味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,小要见到爱良了  Happy☆Lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,小要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你的教练是神崎其方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,小要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我就来  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,再见  爱良
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是其方阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,棱镜天后系列杯第二战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,冬日白雪杯开场了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,本场比赛也聚集了国内精英级的Prism Star
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,其中引人注目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,人气偶像组合MARs的天宫律舞选手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:07:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她是否能在高峰美音与春音爱良之后继续夺冠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,并且  另一位值得关注的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,久里须要选手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,她年仅12岁就在俄罗斯的新人赛桑托贝雷姆杯上获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,其实力到底如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,过去人们想要成为神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,便建造了高不可攀的塔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,连天空都要统治
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是人们最终触怒了神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,塔被神圣的雷电摧毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,失去最重要的东西时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就是重生之时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,从接受所有事物起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,开启新的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来登场的是久里须要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,她到底会为我们展现怎样的舞姿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是其方的舞蹈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么小要会跳和妈妈一样的舞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这支舞和其方成为棱镜天后时跳的一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  小要的教练果然是其方阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:07.65,Prism Jump 橙色,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鲜果篮子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:07.65,Prism Jump 橙色,,0,0,0,,{\fscx65\fscy65\blur3}Fresh Fruits Basket
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy☆Lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,小要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然模仿了爱良的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:38.43,Prism Jump 蓝色,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}星尘流星雨 完美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:38.43,Prism Jump 蓝色,,0,0,0,,{\fscx65\fscy65\blur3}Stardust Shower Perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,大展身手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,连我的技能也模仿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,太可怕了  久里须要的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来  她的得分是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,8280克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,与春音爱良创下的赛季最佳纪录持平
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,非常高的分数啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了  我和爱良一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy☆Lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,挺能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害  小要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她没有跳极光腾跃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是冲着棱镜天后杯去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,爱良的朋友  拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须跳出厉害的舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我要跳极光腾跃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,律舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,终于轮到天宫律舞出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,律舞  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,律舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,律舞  加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,律舞  只要发挥出平时的水平就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,心灵充电
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,律舞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不准跳极光腾跃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,将来你一定能跳出极光腾跃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保证
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但是如果你现在跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,会失去一切的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你是  其方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:25.55,Prism Jump 蓝色,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海豚维纳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:25.55,Prism Jump 蓝色,,0,0,0,,{\fscx65\fscy65\blur3}Dolphin Venus
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我要跳  要跳得非常高  非常壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好  你忍住了呢  律舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,尽可能跳得更远
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:21.32,Prism Jump 红色,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}超级星尘流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:21.32,Prism Jump 红色,,0,0,0,,{\fscx65\fscy65\blur3}Super Stardust Shower
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,落地失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来  律舞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,响
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住了  天宫律舞选手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然落地时失去了平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但最终还是站稳了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,千钧一发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,天宫律舞的得分是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,7290克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,受了落地失败的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是其方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你是来看律舞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,律舞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈  你就是我妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,律舞  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,律舞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这是妈妈做的安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是你留给我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:14:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈  我拿了第一名哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,做得真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,果然必须要跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,极光腾跃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,律舞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道妈妈身上到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,律舞  已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸已经到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸已经不想再失去任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,律舞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,连你也不在了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸就活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么会让爸爸孤零零一个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,从我懂事起  就一直看着爸爸寂寞的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会扔下爸爸不管的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就算跳了极光腾跃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不会离开的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,所以爸爸就放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,律舞
